06:20.210 --> 06:23.168
I studied this case.
I'll never forget it.

06:25.120 --> 06:27.532
This is where the workshop stood.

06:27.540 --> 06:30.282
There was an arch, right here.

06:30.290 --> 06:33.111
He used his workspace as a torture room.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.957
