-What?

12:48.120 --> 12:50.111
"Mom, I know how difficult this must be."

12:50.120 --> 12:51.951
"...difficult this must be."

12:51.960 --> 12:53.996
"Things between us
were never what they should be..."

12:54.000 --> 12:55.319
"...between a mother and her daughter."

12:55.330 --> 12:56.456
