17:42.790 --> 17:46.169
Twelve roses.
One for each girl Jacob killed.

17:47.830 --> 17:52.199
Twelve. Not 13. We found number 13.

17:53.120 --> 17:55.372
You didn't know about her.

17:55.380 --> 17:56.950
