17:56.960 --> 17:58.746
I never said I did.

18:01.210 --> 18:04.327
That was a nice touch,
bringing in the hottie.

18:05.620 --> 18:09.454
You really want to know
if there was others, don't you?

18:09.460 --> 18:12.611
I tell you what. Draw poker.

18:13.330 --> 18:17.243
-You win, I'll give you another girl.
-So there are more?

18:17.250 --> 18:19.878
-Do we have a bet

18:24.380 --> 18:28.111
I get to smell Jennifer's hair.

18:28.120 --> 18:29.667
-No.
-Oh, come on.

18:29.670 --> 18:31.911
All she has to do is lean over
and I get to smell her hair.

18:31.920 --> 18:33.319
No!

18:35.670 --> 18:38.616
-I thought you wanted answers.
-Go to hell.

18:38.960 --> 18:40.666
It's okay, Hotch.

18:42.120 --> 18:45.704
You see that? "It's okay, Hotch."

18:49.460 --> 18:51.166
Come on.

18:55.620 --> 18:58.999
JJ deals. You think I'd let you deal
from your own deck?

19:09.080 --> 19:11.457
