19:17.830 --> 19:19.821
Well, where's the body?

19:22.250 --> 19:25.378
-Do you have any children?
-That's irrelevant.

19:26.420 --> 19:29.207
Do you carry pictures of your children,
Agent Gideon?

19:29.210 --> 19:31.747
